## 5. Data Flow Diagram (for PPT)

```
[Input Text]
     │
     ▼
[Tokenize] → [Model Forward Pass: Layer 0..31]
     │
     │  For each MoE layer:
     │  ├── Gate output (16 expert scores) captured
     │  └── Accumulated into EAM (32×16 matrix)
     │
     │  At Layer 11 (PREDICTION_START_LAYER):
     │  ├── Preprocess EAM[0..11] → 192-dim vector
     │  ├── IVF Search against deduplicated trace (~M entries)
     │  ├── Find most similar trace entry (cos_dist ~0.0015)
     │  └── Create snapshot: top-4 experts per future layer (12..31)
     │
     │  Layers 12..31:
     │  ├── Use snapshot for expert prediction
     │  └── Prefetch expert weights from disk (mmap, background threads)
     │
     ▼
[Generated Token] → repeat for N tokens
```

**Offline pipeline:**
```
[Raw Traces (8.1M EAMs)] → [SemDeDup (K-Means + Cosine Sim)] → [Dedup Traces]
                                                                        │
                                                                        ▼
                                                              [Preprocess: Softmax → L2-norm → Flatten → L2-norm]
                                                                        │
                                                                        ▼
                                                              [Build FAISS IVF Index (nlist=100, nprobe=10)]
                                                                        │
                                                                        ▼
                                                              [Save trace to memmap on disk → Free RAM]
```
